geo_acc <- "GSE119352"
do_download <- T

gse <- getGEO(geo_acc)
datadir <- "input/Gubin"
dir.create(datadir)

series <- paste0(geo_acc, "_series_matrix.txt.gz")
if(do_download){
  getGEOSuppFiles(geo_acc,baseDir=datadir)
  system(paste0("gunzip ",datadir,"/",geo_acc,"/*meta_data.tsv.gz")) 
  
  for (acc in gse[[series]]$geo_accession) {
    dir.create(file.path(datadir, acc))
    getGEOSuppFiles(acc,baseDir=datadir) #untar...
    fns <- list.files(paste0(datadir,"/",acc,"/"))
    for (fn in fns){  #rename to basic names: matrix, genes, barcodes
      system(paste0("mv ",paste0(datadir,"/",acc,"/",fn)," ",paste0(datadir,"/",acc,"/",sub(".*_","",fn,perl = T))))
    }
    system(paste0("gunzip ",datadir,"/",acc,"/*gz"))
    
  }
}

#as.character(gse[[1]]$title[gse[[1]]$geo_accession==acc])

Read the sparse count matrices

data.list <- list()

for (i in 1:length(gse[[series]]$geo_accession)) {
   acc = gse[[series]]$geo_accession[i]
   fname <- paste0(datadir,"/",acc)
   data <- Read10X(fname)
   title <- gse[[1]]$title[i]
   
   c <- gsub(pattern="(\\S+)", replacement=paste0("GU-\\1-",i), colnames(data), perl=TRUE)
   colnames(data) <- c
   
   tmp.seurat <- CreateSeuratObject(counts = data, project = "Gubin", min.cells = 3, min.features = 50)
   tmp.seurat@meta.data$Sample <- acc
   tmp.seurat@meta.data$Condition <- title
   
   data.list[[title]] <- tmp.seurat
   rm(tmp.seurat)
}

names(data.list)

data.list[[1]]$Treatment <- "Control" 
data.list[[2]]$Treatment <- "aPD1"
data.list[[3]]$Treatment <- "aCTLA4"
data.list[[4]]$Treatment <- "aPD1_aCTLA4"

data.seurat.raw <- Reduce(merge, data.list)

scGate for isolating cell subsets

Filter on T cells

data.T <- scGate(data.seurat, gating.model = scGate_DB$mouse$Tcell, sd.out = 5)
plt.ispure <- DimPlot(data.T, group.by =  'is.pure')
plt.ann <- DimPlot(data.T, group.by="scGate.annotation")
plt.ispure + plt.ann

Split by sample and project into TIL atlas

query.list <- SplitObject(data.T, split.by = "Treatment")

ref <- load.reference.map()  #def TIL atlas

query.projected <- make.projection(query.list, ref=ref)
pll <- list()
for (sample in names(query.projected)) {
  
    query.projected[[sample]] <- cellstate.predict(ref=ref, query=query.projected[[sample]])

    pll[[sample]] <- plot.projection(ref=ref, query=query.projected[[sample]], linesize = 0.3) + ggtitle(sample)
}
g <- wrap_plots(pll)
g

ggsave("out/Gubin_Tcell_projection.png", plot=g, width=12, height=8)
gene.panel <- c("Foxp3", "Cd4", "Cd8a", "Tcf7", "Ccr7", "Ifng", "Il2ra",
            "Gzmb", "Gzmk", "Pdcd1", "Havcr2", "Tox", "Mki67")

p <- plot.states.radar(ref=ref, query=query.projected, genes4radar = gene.panel, return=T, min.cells = 30)
plot(p)
#Combined, stacked barplot
states_all <- levels(as.factor(ref$functional.cluster))
stateColors_func <- c("#edbe2a", "#A58AFF", "#53B400", "#F8766D", "#00B6EB", "#d1cfcc", "#FF0000", "#87f6a5", "#e812dd")

m <- matrix(nrow = length(names(query.projected)), ncol = length(states_all))
rownames(m) <- names(query.projected)
colnames(m) <- states_all
m.int <- m
for (i in seq_along(query.projected)) {
  tb <- table(factor(query.projected[[i]]$functional.cluster, levels = states_all))
  m[i, ] <- tb * 100/sum(tb)
  m.int[i, ] <- tb
}

melt <- melt(m)
melt.int <- melt(m.int)
melt <- cbind(melt, melt.int$value)
colnames(melt) <- c("Sample", "Cell_state", "Percent","Ncells")

g <- ggplot(melt, aes(x = Sample, y = Percent, fill = Cell_state, Ncells = Ncells)) + geom_bar(stat = "identity", 
    position = "stack") + scale_fill_manual(values = stateColors_func) + 
    theme_light() + theme(legend.position = "right") + ylab("Percentage of cells")
g

ggsave("Gubin.state.composition.combined.png", plot=g, height=4.5, width=6)

Isolate MoMacDC cells

data.seurat <- readRDS("aux/Gubin_CD45_clean.rds")

data.seurat <- scGate(data.seurat, gating.model = scGate_DB$mouse$Tcell, sd.out = 1000, sd.in = 10)

features <- c("T.cell_scGate","Stromal.cell_scGate","MoMacDC_scGate","NK.cell_scGate")
FeaturePlot(data.seurat, reduction="umap", features=features, order = T,ncol = 2)
#Unsupervised clustering
set.seed(12345)

which.red <- "pca"

resol=0.3
ndim=15
data.seurat <- FindNeighbors(data.seurat, reduction = which.red, dims = 1:ndim)

data.seurat <- FindClusters(data.seurat, resolution = resol)

DimPlot(data.seurat, reduction="umap", group.by = "seurat_clusters", label = T) + NoLegend()
VlnPlot(data.seurat, group.by = "seurat_clusters", features = features)

Select myeloid clusters

means.T <- sapply(levels(data.seurat$seurat_clusters), function(x) {
    mean(data.seurat@meta.data[data.seurat$seurat_clusters == x, "T.cell_scGate"])
})
means.MoMacDC <- sapply(levels(data.seurat$seurat_clusters), function(x) {
    mean(data.seurat@meta.data[data.seurat$seurat_clusters == x, "MoMacDC_scGate"])
})

clusters.pass1 <- names(means.T[means.T < 0.2])
clusters.pass2 <- names(means.MoMacDC[means.MoMacDC > 0.3])
clusters.pass <- intersect(clusters.pass1, clusters.pass2)

data.seurat$Broad.Cell.Type <- "other"
data.seurat$Broad.Cell.Type[data.seurat$seurat_clusters %in% clusters.pass] <- "MoMacDC"
data.seurat$Broad.Cell.Type[data.seurat$seurat_clusters %in% 3] <- "NK"
data.seurat$Broad.Cell.Type[data.seurat$seurat_clusters %in% c(2,3,9)] <- "T.cell"
data.seurat$Broad.Cell.Type[data.seurat$seurat_clusters %in% 10] <- "stromal"

table(data.seurat$Broad.Cell.Type)
saveRDS(data.seurat, "aux/Gubin_CD45_clean_annotated.rds")
data.myel <- subset(data.seurat, subset=seurat_clusters %in% clusters.pass)
data.myel
